    "## ðŸŽ¯ Challenge 1: Sorting Movies by Rating\n",
    "\n",
    "Let's find the highest-rated movies first! We can use `ORDER BY` to sort our results:\n",
    "```sql\n",
    "SELECT title, rating\n",
    "FROM movies\n",
    "ORDER BY rating DESC;  -- DESC means descending (highest to lowest)\n",
    "```\n",
    "\n",
    "ðŸ’¡ Use `ASC` for ascending order (lowest to highest) - this is actually the default if you don't specify!"
