    "## ðŸŽ¯ Challenge 2: Finding the Top 5 Movies\n",
    "\n",
    "Sometimes we only want to see a few results. The `LIMIT` clause helps us with that:\n",
    "```sql\n",
    "SELECT title, rating\n",
    "FROM movies\n",
    "ORDER BY rating DESC\n",
    "LIMIT 5;\n",
    "```\n",
    "\n",
    "Try finding the 3 most recent movies in our database!"
